				<td colspan="2"><span>If you haven't done it, be sure and check out all the guides. A lot of what bards can do is not intuitive to most people, especially someone new to EQ.
<br />

<br />
The guides show a myriad of ways to play your bard, and will make it clear that if you devote the time to learn all the tequniques, or at least the ones that appeal to you, you'll be playing one of the hardest and best classes in the game. 
<br />

<br />
Certainly bards are the most versatile.
<br />

<br />
Please don't hesitate to ask questions, try the search feature (it works better here than on EZ Boards), and....
<br />

<br />

<br />
Welcome!
