			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>or map songs to your f1-f8 keys and remapp those targetting keys (if you use them a lot...or just leave along if alt-f1 works for you).
<br />

<br />
Macros with delays don't work great for mostbards (some still claim success) because there is no fail safe for missed notes like there is for fizzles. A failed macro can cause 3-18 seconds of pretty much non interuptable bard silence--longer if you use a programmable gamepad (/time command, when macroed from hotkeys will reportedly interupt macro pauses....i haven't tried it).
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
