				<td colspan="2"><span>Regarding the spreadsheet... Make sure you notice there is a 2nd tab on it, called &quot;Song Details&quot;.
<br />

<br />
As a younger bard, you might want to use that one for a while.  The first page is geared towards higher end bards with lots of equipment, epic, AA's, etc.
<br />

<br />
(The most important thing about the 1st page, is that there is a &quot;key&quot; to what each of the 4 numbers mean at the top... look for it.)
<br />

<br />
